{"data":[{"date":"23:41 12/08","title":"HLV Manuel Pellegrini: \"Liverpool l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t Premier League\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/hlv-manuel-pellegrini-sau-tran-thua-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Manuel Pellegrini sau tr\u1eadn thua Liverpool th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn West Ham ch\u01a1i ch\u01b0a t\u1ed1t, x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t Premier League.</h2><h2>X\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 nh\u01b0ng ngay trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, West Ham ph\u1ea3i n\u1ebfm tr\u00e1i \u0111\u1eafng khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua Liverpool v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 0-4. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea9y West Ham xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng sau v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Manuel Pellegrini sau tr\u1eadn thua Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Manuel Pellegrini sau tr\u1eadn thua Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/hlv-manuel-pellegrini-sau-tran-thua-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Manuel Pellegrini sau tr\u1eadn thua Liverpool th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn West Ham x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Manuel Pellegrini sau tr\u1eadn thua Liverpool l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i: \"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n. West Ham \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t, ch\u01b0a t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngo\u00e0i kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian 15 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p hai. Liverpool x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u00edch c\u1ef1c. \u0110\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi, ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i, ho\u1eb7c ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i hay nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u\".\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u1ec1 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng HLV Pellegrini cho r\u1eb1ng thua v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 4-0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn v\u1edbi West Ham. Vi\u1ec7c Sadio Mane \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong th\u1ebf vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn HLV Pellegrini t\u1ecf r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf th\u1ebf vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb\" - HLV Pellegrini ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n: \"Vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 hai mang \u0111\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng t\u00e2m l\u00fd l\u1edbn h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 b\u1edfi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng trong hi\u1ec7p hai. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng b\u1ecb d\u1eabn 2-0 ph\u1ea3i kh\u00e1c 1-0\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u sau, West Ham s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n ti\u1ebfp Bournemouth.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Liverpool 4-0 West Ham:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sadio-mane-sau-tran-thang-west-ham-liverpool-chua-muon-dung-lai-172-194342.html\">Sadio Mane sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng West Ham: Liverpool ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-liverpool-40-west-ham-172-194339.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn Liverpool 4-0 West Ham</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-liverpool-vs-west-ham-40-highlights-premier-league-2018-326-194338.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Liverpool 4-0 West Ham (V\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jurgen-klopp-ly-giai-doi-hinh-xuat-phat-liverpool-tran-mo-man-premier-league-172-194337.html\">Jurgen Klopp l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t Liverpool tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-vo-dich-premier-league-alisson-se-la-ban-hop-dong-cua-mua-giai-172-194332.html\">Liverpool v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League, Alisson s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ket-qua-liverpool-vs-west-ham-1282018-172-194329.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Liverpool vs West Ham tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2294","checkdouble":"194343"},{"date":"00:41 13/08","title":"Ra m\u1eaft \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d Liverpool \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u00f3 ng\u1ee3i ca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/james-milner-khen-ngoi-naby-keita.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>James Milner khen ng\u1ee3i Naby Keita. \u0110\u1ed9i ph\u00f3 c\u1ee7a Liverpool tin b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham v\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u00f2n gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Keita ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Premier League, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng 4-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, Sadio Mane l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap, Mohamed Salah v\u00e0 Daniel Sturridge c\u00f9ng ghi 1 b\u00e0n gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Merseyside c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Anfield.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong \u0111\u00f3, t\u00e2n binh Naby Keita c\u1ee7a Liverpool kh\u00f4ng ghi t\u00ean m\u00ecnh l\u00ean b\u1ea3ng \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn The Kop v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb RB Leipzig v\u1eabn l\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. Anh c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf s\u1eafp m\u1eb7t s\u00e2n, \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p l\u1edbn v\u00e0o kh\u00e2u thu h\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"James Milner khen ng\u1ee3i Naby Keita h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"James Milner khen ng\u1ee3i Naby Keita h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/James-Milner-khen-ngoi-Naby-Keita-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Liverpool v\u00f9i d\u1eadp West Ham 4-0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Keita, kh\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1eeb xa c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. V\u00e0 sau c\u00f9ng, anh c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham ngay trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c Milner ca ng\u1ee3i</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi West Ham, ch\u00ednh Keita \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t. V\u00e0 sau tr\u1eadn, \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u00f3 James Milner khen ng\u1ee3i Naby Keita h\u1ebft l\u1eddi. \u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ngay l\u00fac n\u00e0y\u201d, Milner n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Sky Sports.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Naby Keita\" title=\"tien ve Naby Keita\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/james-milner-khen-ngoi-naby-keita.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>James Milner khen ng\u1ee3i Naby Keita</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKeita c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. Khi ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi, m\u1ed9t phong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i m\u1edbi m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh dung c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc th\u1ebf n\u00e0o trong v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng t\u1edbi v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c tr\u1ea3i qua nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian ch\u01a1i h\u01a1n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMilner ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c v\u1ec1 Keita: \u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thu h\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng, \u0111i b\u00f3ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nhanh nh\u1eb9n. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mang v\u1ec1.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cS\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh l\u1edbn h\u01a1n \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n. B\u1ea1n nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ch\u00e0ng trai tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t, s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Liverpool 4-0 West Ham tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-klopp-thong-bao-thoi-diem-lovren-binh-phuc-chan-thuong-172-194345.html\">HLV Klopp th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m trung v\u1ec7 Liverpool b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-manuel-pellegrini-sau-tran-thua-liverpool-172-194343.html\">HLV Manuel Pellegrini: Liverpool l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t Premier League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sadio-mane-sau-tran-thang-west-ham-liverpool-chua-muon-dung-lai-172-194342.html\">Sadio Mane sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng West Ham: Liverpool ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-liverpool-40-west-ham-172-194339.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn Liverpool 4-0 West Ham</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ket-qua-liverpool-vs-west-ham-1282018-172-194329.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Liverpool vs West Ham tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2293","checkdouble":"194344"},{"date":"00:37 13/08","title":"HLV Klopp th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m trung v\u1ec7 Liverpool b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/hlv-klopp-thong-bao-thoi-diem-lovren-binh-phuc-chan-thuong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Petr Cech tin r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Arsenal s\u1ebd tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n sau tr\u1eadn thua Man City ngay t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Emirates v\u1eeba qua.</h2><h2>Arsenal thua t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Raheem Sterling v\u00e0 Bernardo Silva \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Man City c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Unai Emery.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng pressing ngay t\u1eeb ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Man City. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn t\u1eeb ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. Nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i test nh\u01b0 Man City l\u00fac n\u00e0y qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi Arsenal.</div>\r\n<h2>Cech \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Petr Cech \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i sau tr\u1eadn thua Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Petr Cech \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i sau tr\u1eadn thua Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/cech-thua-man-city-giup-arsenal-truong-thanh-hon.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Cech c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Petr Cech \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Anh cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Arsenal s\u1ebd tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh sau tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thua th\u00eam v\u00e0 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thua v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t \u00edt h\u01a1n. Trong hi\u1ec7p hai, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m trong kh\u00e2u tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng. V\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTrong 1/3 s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m pha b\u00f3ng. Khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin nh\u01b0 Man City th\u00ec m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n lu\u00f4n lu\u00f4n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u00ecn chung, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f3 tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ec7c m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 th\u1eadt t\u1ec7 khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra trong hi\u1ec7p hai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV m\u1edbi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i m\u1edbi v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh nhanh h\u01a1n\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVideo t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Man City:<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278994\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/08/13/arsenal-mancity-.mp4&autoplay=false\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"340\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Man City:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-arsenal-02-man-city-172-194347.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn Arsenal 0-2 Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-arsenal-vs-man-city-02-highlights-premier-league-2018-326-194346.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Arsenal 0-2 Man City (V\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2292","checkdouble":"194345"},{"date":"01:01 13/08","title":"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn Arsenal 0-2 Man City","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-arsenal-02-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Arsenal 0-2 Man City v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n- Arsenal ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng sau 8 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u1eeba qua (thua 3, h\u00f2a 3).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Man City b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong 10 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh (th\u1eafng 9, h\u00f2a 1).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Unai Emery l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong s\u1ed1 6 HLV g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Arsenal (t\u00ednh c\u1ea3 t\u1ea1m quy\u1ec1n) \u0111\u00e3 thua trong tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn Arsenal 0-2 Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn Arsenal 0-2 Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/Sterling-ghi-ban-mo-ty-cho-Man-City.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Sterling c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 50 t\u1ea1i Premier League trong tr\u1eadn Arsenal 0-2 Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n- Pep Guardiola v\u1eabn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ed c\u00f9ng Unai Emery tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, bao g\u1ed3m th\u1eafng 7, h\u00f2a 4 sau 11 tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Matteo Guendouzi l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 27 c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p ch\u01a1i cho Arsenal \u1edf Premier League, b\u1eb1ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Newcastle.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Stephan Lichtsteiner l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t ra m\u1eaft t\u1ea1i Premier League cho Arsenal (34 tu\u1ed5i 208 ng\u00e0y).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Raheem Sterling \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 50 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Premier League, t\u00ednh c\u1ea3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn Arsenal 0-2 Man City.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Sterling \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tham gia v\u00e0o 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 12 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Premier League, ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 5 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o 7 l\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Benjamin Mendy \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 2 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o trong 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2, sau tr\u1eadn vs Nice khi kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Monaco th\u00e1ng 2 n\u0103m 2017.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Bernardo Silva \u0111\u00e3 ghi 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 7 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn </strong><strong>Arsenal 0-2 Man City (V\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19):<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278994\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/08/13/arsenal-mancity-.mp4&autoplay=false\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"340\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2291","checkdouble":"194347"},{"date":"01:45 13/08","title":"3 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Liverpool v\u00f9i d\u1eadp West Ham 4 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/3-ly-do-giup-liverpool-vui-dap-west-ham-4-ban-khong-go.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 4-0. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y r\u1eaby t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u1edbi The Kop. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 3 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Klopp gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</h2><h2>B\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u1eabn gi\u1eef phong \u0111\u1ed9\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Liverpool v\u00f9i d\u1eadp West Ham 4 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Liverpool v\u00f9i d\u1eadp West Ham 4 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/James-Milner-khen-ngoi-Naby-Keita-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>B\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool ch\u01a1i qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Salah, Mane v\u00e0 Firmino c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/liverpool-2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool</span> v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. H\u1ecd li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng pha di chuy\u1ec3n lu\u1ed3n sau l\u01b0ng h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 West Ham v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb k\u00e9o kh\u1ecfi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMane \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Declan Rice trong nhi\u1ec1u pha b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t. Nh\u1edd v\u1eady m\u00e0 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 bi\u00ean v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMichail Antonio li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecf qua nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng l\u1ed7 h\u1ed5ng l\u1edbn b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang ph\u1ea3i. Nh\u1edd v\u1eady m\u00e0 Andy Robertson c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ed9i bom t\u1eeb v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 Salah m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a West Ham c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 m\u01a1 ng\u1ee7 \u1edf t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec7m b\u00f3ng c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Mane sau pha c\u0103ng ngang c\u1ee7a Milner cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t. L\u1ed7i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a &ldquo;B\u00faa t\u1ea1&rdquo; c\u00f2n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 n\u00e9t trong hai b\u00e0n thua sau \u0111\u00f3 khi h\u1ecd li\u00ean t\u1ee5c m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 Mane c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Salah tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi West Ham v\u1eeba qua ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng xuy\u00ean th\u1ee7ng h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 West Ham kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 gi\u00fap cho The Kop d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p \u0103n \u00fd\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool vs West Ham\" title=\"Liverpool vs West Ham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Liverpool kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb West Ham</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Liverpool th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u0103n \u00fd c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd thi tho\u1ea3ng b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn, \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 b\u1ecb thua nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi West Ham t\u1ea1i Anfield cho th\u1ea5y hai tuy\u1ebfn n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n ra sao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 v\u1ec7 Alexander-Arnold, Joe Gomez, Van Dijk v\u00e0 Robertson ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p kh\u00e1 nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng v\u1edbi Wijnaldum, Milner v\u00e0 Naby Keita \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n m\u1ecdi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a West Ham.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nWijnaldum \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i trong vai tr\u00f2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ee5 trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t. Anh c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n l\u00ean tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t. Anh \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1edbi 92% \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua. Nh\u01b0ng Wijnaldum v\u1eabn n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u1edf kh\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. S\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac \u0111\u00fang ch\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan \u0111\u00e3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nMilner g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 v\u00e0 gi\u00fap nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool m\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0 h\u01a1n. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Naby Keita c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft khi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 bi\u00ean c\u1ee7a The Kop c\u0169ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 l\u01a1 l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Joe Gomez v\u00e0 Van Dijk c\u0169ng k\u1ec1m t\u1ecfa t\u1ed1t Arnautovic v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00c1o g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 b\u1ecb c\u00f4 l\u1eadp ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u1ecfi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn chung, vi\u1ec7c tuy\u1ebfn d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Liverpool ch\u01a1i \u0103n \u00fd h\u01a1n \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng West Ham g\u00e2y nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0o th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/james-milner-khen-ngoi-naby-keita-172-194344.html\">Ra m\u1eaft \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; Liverpool \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u00f3 ng\u1ee3i ca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sadio-mane-sau-tran-thang-west-ham-liverpool-chua-muon-dung-lai-172-194342.html\">Sadio Mane sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng West Ham: Liverpool ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Naby Keita ch\u01a1i qu\u00e1 hay\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Naby Keita\" title=\"Naby Keita\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Naby Keita ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Premier League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng Naby Keita v\u1eabn l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1eadm n\u00e9t nh\u1ea5t trong ng\u00e0y ch\u00e0o s\u00e2n Anfield. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Leipzig cho th\u1ea5y h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 thi\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u00f4i khi v\u1eabn b\u1ecb ch\u00ea l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n an to\u00e0n nh\u01b0 chuy\u1ec1n sang hai h\u00e0nh lang bi\u00ean. Nh\u01b0ng khi c\u00f3 Keita, \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd tr\u1edf n\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Guinea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng x\u1ed9c th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ee1 n\u00e0o v\u00e0 g\u00e2y ra nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e2m th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Keita \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf ra kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng cho Robertson b\u0103ng xu\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 tung \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho Salah trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKeita c\u0169ng thu h\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n nh\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng, ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0 t\u00ec \u0111\u00e8 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Liverpool chuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i t\u1eeb th\u1ee7 sang c\u00f4ng nhanh v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3u qu\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Mane, Keita li\u00ean t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c cho h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 West Ham v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng x\u00e2y x\u1ea9m m\u1eb7t m\u00e0y su\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n v\u1eeba qua l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i t\u1ea1i sao Keita l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Klopp \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady. Qua th\u1eddi gian, khi \u0111\u00e3 hi\u1ec3u m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng Premier League h\u01a1n, Keita ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f2n tr\u1edf n\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. S\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Keita qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool l\u00ean m\u1ed9t t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam video tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Liverpool vs West Ham:</strong><br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278984\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/08/12/liverpool-westham-1534084348.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"340\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2290","checkdouble":"194348"},{"date":"02:03 13/08","title":"Cech: \"Tr\u1eadn thua Man City gi\u00fap Arsenal tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/cech-thua-man-city-giup-arsenal-truong-thanh-hon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Petr Cech tin r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Arsenal s\u1ebd tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n sau tr\u1eadn thua Man City ngay t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Emirates v\u1eeba qua.</h2><h2>Arsenal thua t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Raheem Sterling v\u00e0 Bernardo Silva \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Man City c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Unai Emery.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng pressing ngay t\u1eeb ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Man City. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn t\u1eeb ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. Nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i test nh\u01b0 Man City l\u00fac n\u00e0y qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi Arsenal.</div>\r\n<h2>Cech \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Petr Cech \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i sau tr\u1eadn thua Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Petr Cech \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i sau tr\u1eadn thua Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/cech-thua-man-city-giup-arsenal-truong-thanh-hon.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Cech c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Petr Cech \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Anh cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Arsenal s\u1ebd tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh sau tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thua th\u00eam v\u00e0 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thua v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t \u00edt h\u01a1n. Trong hi\u1ec7p hai, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m trong kh\u00e2u tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng. V\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTrong 1/3 s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m pha b\u00f3ng. Khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin nh\u01b0 Man City th\u00ec m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n lu\u00f4n lu\u00f4n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u00ecn chung, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f3 tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ec7c m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 th\u1eadt t\u1ec7 khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra trong hi\u1ec7p hai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV m\u1edbi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i m\u1edbi v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh nhanh h\u01a1n\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVideo t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Man City:<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278994\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/08/13/arsenal-mancity-.mp4&autoplay=false\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"340\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Man City:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-arsenal-02-man-city-172-194347.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn Arsenal 0-2 Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-arsenal-vs-man-city-02-highlights-premier-league-2018-326-194346.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Arsenal 0-2 Man City (V\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2289","checkdouble":"194349"},{"date":"02:34 13/08","title":"Sterling l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i m\u00e0n \u0103n m\u1eebng khi\u00eau kh\u00edch tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/sterling-ly-giai-man-an-mung-khieu-khich-o-tran-gap-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Raheem Sterling t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 vui m\u1eebng sau khi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Arsenal \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a anh trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n World Cup 2018.</h2><h2>Sterling g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Arsenal v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-0 trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n \u1edf Premier League. V\u00e0 Sterling \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p b\u00e0n khai th\u00f4ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t pha solo tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tung c\u00fa s\u00fat xa h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Petr Cech.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed1i l\u1eadp ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Sterling t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Khi \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng g\u00e2y \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a Sterling h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ec1u k\u1ebft th\u00fac b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 thi\u1ebfu ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sterling l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i m\u00e0n \u0103n m\u1eebng khi\u00eau kh\u00edch tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sterling l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i m\u00e0n \u0103n m\u1eebng khi\u00eau kh\u00edch tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/sterling-ly-giai-man-an-mung-khieu-khich-o-tran-gap-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Sterling \u0103n m\u1eebng khi\u00eau kh\u00edch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, Sterling \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t 1 tay l\u00ean tai \u00fd mu\u1ed1n h\u1ecfi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch anh gi\u1edd \u0111ang \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u. V\u00e0 trong b\u00e0i ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb r\u00f5 h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c \u0103n m\u1eebng n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch t\u00f4i n\u00ean t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c \u0103n m\u1eebng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Nh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 sao t\u00f4i c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. B\u1edfi v\u00ec t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 b\u1edfi s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00ecnh ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Bernardo Silva vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Bernardo Silva l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-0 cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf ph\u00fat 64. V\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a The Citizens.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 Arsenal l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u01b0 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Man City:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cech-thua-man-city-giup-arsenal-truong-thanh-hon-172-194349.html\">Cech: Tr\u1eadn thua Man City gi\u00fap Arsenal tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-arsenal-02-man-city-172-194347.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn Arsenal 0-2 Man City</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2288","checkdouble":"194350"},{"date":"03:59 13/08","title":"C\u1ef1u sao M.U n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Arsenal 0-2 Man City?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/gary-neville-noi-ve-tran-arsenal-02-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi Sky Sports, c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean CLB M.U, Gary Neville \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn HLV Unai Emery c\u1ea7n 3, 4 k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00f3a s\u1ea1ch \u2018di s\u1ea3n\u2019 m\u00e0 HLV Wenger \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.</h2><h2>Gary Neville n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Arsenal 0-2 Man City</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gary Neville n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Arsenal 0-2 Man City  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gary Neville n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Arsenal 0-2 Man City  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/gary-neville-noi-ve-tran-arsenal-02-man-city.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gary Neville cho r\u1eb1ng Unai Emery c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i\u00a0</span>Arsenal</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n k\u00e9m vui sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110KV\u0110 Man City ngay t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Emirates.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n t\u1eeb xa y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 khi b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Xhaka v\u00e0 Guendouzi kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Petr Cech ph\u1ea3i hai l\u1ea7n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng sau nh\u1eefng c\u00fa s\u00fat xa uy l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao Man xanh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, c\u1ef1u sao M.U Gary Neville \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i tr\u00ean Sky Sports: \"T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Emery s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn ra \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ef3 qu\u00e1i m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi\u00a0Man xanh. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i s\u1ef1 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n. Emery s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n 3,4 m\u00f9a chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. V\u00ec th\u1ebf \u00f4ng \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n nh\u01b0 15 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn\u201d. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n m\u00ecnh, c\u1ef1u sao Arsenal Paul Merson l\u1ea1i nghi ng\u1edd vi\u1ec7c HLV Emery chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Stephan Lichtsteiner n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 34 tu\u1ed5i. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cUnai \u0111\u00e3 mua nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 Arsenal c\u1ea7n. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n th\u00eam nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. <o:p></o:p>\u0110\u1ea5y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Lichtsteiner c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf Arsenal, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1ea7n 35 tu\u1ed5i... <br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 bao nhi\u00eau c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady \u1edf Premier League? \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00f3? Tuy nhi\u00ean, Unai \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m, r\u1ed3i m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd kh\u00e1c. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian\u201d, Paul Merson chia s\u1ebb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n k\u00e9m vui tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Unai Emery \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 s\u1ebd \u00edt c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec3m khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 Chelsea \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-arsenal-vs-man-city-02-highlights-premier-league-2018-326-194346.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/clip-arsenal-vs-man-city-02-highlights-premier-league-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-arsenal-vs-man-city-02-highlights-premier-league-2018-326-194346.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Arsenal 0-2 Man City (V\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19)</span><br>\r\nMan City ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2287","checkdouble":"194351"},{"date":"05:48 13/08","title":"V\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Si\u00eau C\u00fap, Lionel Messi l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1edbi trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/vo-dich-sieu-cup-lionel-messi-lap-ky-luc-moi-trong-mau-ao-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Sevilla, Lionel Messi l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1edbi v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 danh hi\u1ec7u gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barcelona v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam m\u1ed9t Si\u00eau C\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0o b\u1ed9 s\u01b0u t\u1eadp.</h2><h2>Lionel Messi l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n, Barca \u0111\u00e3 thu v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 ban \u0111\u1ea7u khi gi\u00e0nh Si\u00eau C\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Sevilla v\u1edbi m\u00e0n l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Gerard Pique v\u00e0 Ousmane Dembele l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng cho Barca.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lionel Messi lap ky luc ve so danh hieu gianh duoc trong mau ao Barca\" title=\"Lionel Messi l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 danh hi\u1ec7u gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/vo-dich-sieu-cup-lionel-messi-lap-ky-luc-moi-trong-mau-ao-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Lionel Messi l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 danh hi\u1ec7u gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barca</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ghi b\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng Messi l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh t\u1ef1u l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t. Si\u00eau C\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha 2018 gi\u00fap Lionel Messi l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1edbi, tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Barcelona.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Leo&quot; t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu 33 danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn nh\u1ecf, v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh Andres Iniesta v\u1ed1n c\u00f3 32 danh hi\u1ec7u tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gia nh\u1eadp Vissel Kobe (Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u00e0 s\u01b0u t\u1eadp danh hi\u1ec7u<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s\u1ed1 33 danh hi\u1ec7u gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f9ng Barca, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Si\u00eau C\u00fap th\u1ee9 8 c\u1ee7a Lionel Messi. Ngo\u00e0i ra, &quot;Leo&quot; \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 9 l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch La Liga, gi\u00e0nh C\u00fap nh\u00e0 vua t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 7 l\u1ea7n, b\u1ed1n l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League, 3 l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Si\u00eau C\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u00e0 Club World Cup c\u00f9ng v\u00e0o c\u00e1c n\u0103m 2009, 2011 v\u00e0 2015.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, Messi \u0111\u00e3 5 l\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng, b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi Cristiano Ronaldo. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 5 l\u1ea7n, Messi \u0111\u1ec1u gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1edd nh\u1eefng g\u00ec l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f9ng Barcelona.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Messi, hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thu\u1ed9c &quot;th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 1987&quot; c\u1ee7a Barca l\u00e0 Gerard Pique v\u00e0 Sergio Busquets khi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 28 danh hi\u1ec7u trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia. Xavi Hernandez, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn nh\u1ea5t cho Barca c\u0169ng c\u00f3 25 danh hi\u1ec7u tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ra \u0111i v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2015.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-sevilla-12-barca-sieu-cup-tbn-2018-328-194358.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/video-tong-hop-sevilla-12-barca-sieu-cup-tbn-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-sevilla-12-barca-sieu-cup-tbn-2018-328-194358.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Sevilla 1-2 Barca (Si\u00eau c\u00fap TBN 2018)</span><br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 c\u0169ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng song m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, Blaugrana \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y t\u00ednh hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 tri\u1ebft...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/sevilla-vs-barca-sieu-cup-tbn-2018-dem-nay-372-194340.html\">Sevilla 1-2 Barca: Messi v\u00e0 c\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi b\u1eb1ng danh hi\u1ec7u Si\u00eau c\u00fap TBN</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nhan-dinh-sevilla-vs-barca-3h-ngay-138-co-messi-la-co-tat-ca-180-194294.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sevilla vs Barca (3h ng\u00e0y 13/8): C\u00f3 Messi l\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-108-messi-chinh-thuc-tro-thanh-tan-doi-truong-barca-184-194199.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 10/8: Messi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/cuoc-chien-ronaldo-vs-messi-nong-lan-sang-ca-khoan-du-thuyen-188-193849.html\">Cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn Ronaldo vs Messi n\u00f3ng lan sang c\u1ea3 kho\u1ea3n ... du thuy\u1ec1n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tro-thanh-dong-doi-messi-vidal-len-tieng-cam-on-hum-xam-180-193716.html\">Tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Messi, Vidal l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3m \u01a1n H\u00f9m x\u00e1m</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/thu-mon-barcelona-tham-vong-qua-mat-ca-messi-180-192583.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Barcelona tham v\u1ecdng qua m\u1eb7t c\u1ea3 Messi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2286","checkdouble":"194357"},{"date":"06:01 13/08","title":"5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Man City tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/13/5-diem-nhan-sau-chien-thang-thuyet-phuc-cua-man-city-truoc-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ngay t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Arsenal, Man City \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 2-0. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 bi\u1ebfn h\u00f3a \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Arsenal 0-2 Man City n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>1. Arsenal \u0111\u1ea7y n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c, nh\u01b0ng&hellip;</h2>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ea7y quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m. D\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 t\u1ea1i Emirates, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 t\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ea7y nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng pha x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c cao. HLV Unai Emery ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u00e1p s\u00e1t nhanh, g\u1eaft v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Man City g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng th\u1eddi gian tr\u00f4i qua, Man City ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc h\u01a1n. H\u1ecd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng k\u00e9o gi\u00e3n ph\u00f2ng tuy\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a Arsenal v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. T\u1eeb m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Benjamin Mendy b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, Raheem Sterling c\u1eaft v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9, qua m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p l\u00e0m ng\u1ee1 ng\u00e0ng c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Arsenal.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Man City tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Man City tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/5-diem-nhan-sau-chien-thang-thuyet-phuc-cua-Man-City-truoc-Arsenal-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">B\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a Sterling \u0111\u00e1nh tan t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ee7a Arsenal</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ai ng\u1edd Sterling l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tung c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 k\u1ef3 \u1ea3o t\u1edbi v\u1eady. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t mi\u1ebfng \u0111\u00e1nh c\u00f3 t\u00ednh to\u00e1n c\u1ee7a Man City. Sau khi chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng cho Sterling, Mendy di chuy\u1ec3n nhanh v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m k\u00e9o theo s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb \u0111\u00e2y, Sterling r\u1ea5t nhanh c\u1eaft v\u00e0o trong v\u00e0 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Petr Cech. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Arsenal 0-2 Man City. Trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, Man City th\u00eam ph\u1ea7n h\u1ee9ng kh\u1edfi v\u00e0 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Bernardo Silva ph\u00fat 64.</div>\r\n<h2>2. Emery \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng</h2>\r\nV\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n, s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 Arsenal s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City l\u00e0 4-2-3-1. Tuy nhi\u00ean, do h\u1ecd l\u00f9i qu\u00e1 s\u00e2u, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1eafm Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang b\u1ecb c\u00f4 l\u1eadp \u1edf ph\u00eda tr\u00ean. B\u1ed9 ba ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Gabon bu\u1ed9c l\u00f2ng ph\u1ea3i tham gia thu h\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t t\u1eeb c\u00e1c v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch v\u00e0 qu\u00ean lu\u00f4n ki\u1ebfn thi\u1ebft cho anh.<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Emery\" title=\"HLV Emery\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/HLV-Emery.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Emery qu\u00e1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Arsenal 0-2 Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ea5t d\u00e0i l\u00ean cho Aubameyang c\u1ee7a Arsenal c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng khi n\u00e0o \u0111\u00fang t\u1ea7m. B\u00f3ng lu\u00f4n \u0111i qu\u00e1 s\u00e2u khi\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 14 tr\u1edf n\u00ean hoang mang \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ed9i nghi\u1ec7p. C\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Auba t\u1edbi t\u1eeb n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a anh v\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111i thi\u1ebfu ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nSang hi\u1ec7p 2, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m h\u01a1n t\u1eeb Arsenal. Ch\u00ednh \u00e1p l\u1ef1c pressing ngay ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Man City m\u1eafc m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 sai l\u1ea7m. Nh\u1eefng Alexandre Lacazette hay Mesut Ozil \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i song \u00edt ra c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u0169ng g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n v\u1edbi Arsenal.</div>\r\n<h2>3. Man City kh\u00f4ng cho Arsenal l\u00e0m b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb s\u00e2n nh\u00e0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Emery tin r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng n\u01a1i ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ch\u1eadm r\u00e3i s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Arsenal h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf r\u1ee7i ro tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u0169i c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t nhanh nh\u1eb9n v\u00e0 bi\u1ebfn h\u00f3a. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u1eeb th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Petr Cech cho t\u1edbi b\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tho\u00e1t \u00e1p s\u00e1t t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal vs Man City Bernardo Silva vs Xhaka\" title=\"Arsenal vs Man City Bernardo Silva vs Xhaka\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/Arsenal-0-2-Man-City-Pep-Team-khong-ngu-quen-tren-chien-thang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Man City c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u00e1p s\u00e1t h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Arsenal r\u1ea5t nhanh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed7i khi h\u1ecd c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man City \u0111\u1ec1u l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c. Qu\u1ea3 nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n. Su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa, Cech \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh &ldquo;t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3&rdquo; v\u1edbi pha x\u1eed l\u00fd h\u1edb h\u00eanh. N\u1ebfu b\u00f3ng \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi, sai s\u00f3t n\u00e0y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd \u00e1m \u1ea3nh anh trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng Cech c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i sai l\u1ea7m m\u00e0 Emery thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp. \u0110\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng Granit Xhaka hay Guendouzi c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u thi\u1ebfu ch\u00fat n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1 cho b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Man City.</div>\r\n<h2>4. HLV Guardiola \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh r\u1ea5t nhanh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00fat 54, HLV Emery quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00fat Aaron Ramsey v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o Alexandre Lacazette. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua v\u1edbi th\u1eddi gian m\u1edbi k\u1ecbp l\u00e0nh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Man City. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m v\u1edbi Ramsey, Emery c\u0169ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m c\u1eb7p Lacazette v\u00e0 Aubameyang song h\u00e0nh trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Pep Guardiola\" title=\"HLV Pep Guardiola\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/HLV-Pep-Guardiola.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Guardiola cho th\u1ea5y nh\u00e3n quan chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt t\u1ed1t</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c. Lacazette gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng Aubameyang kh\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 k\u00e8m c\u1eb7p s\u00e1t sao c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Man City. Anh th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tung c\u00fa vu\u1ed1t b\u00f3ng ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m Arsenal ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0i ph\u00fat sau khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n song \u0111i ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ed9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay sau \u0111\u00f3, Guardiola \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch tung Kevin De Bruyne thay Riyad Mahrez ngay c\u1ea3 khi tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Algeria chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c. V\u00e0 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e2y, s\u1ef1 c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a De Bruyne \u0111\u00e3 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y Man City. Ph\u00fat 64, Mendy c\u0103ng ngang v\u1eeba t\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ec3 Bernardo Silva x\u1eed l\u00fd m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea1m tung n\u00f3c l\u01b0\u1edbi Arsenal.<br>\r\n<h2>5. C\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh Arsenal c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Emery ra m\u1eaft Arsenal, h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ch\u00e0o s\u00e2n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 Sokratis, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Stephan Lichtsteiner v\u00e0 c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m Guendouzi, Lucas Torreira. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 Sokratis. Trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Hy L\u1ea1p th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kinh nghi\u1ec7m song ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u0103n \u00fd v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c Mustafi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Guendouzi\" title=\"Guendouzi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/hlv-emery-benh-vuc-hoc-tro-sau-that-bai-truoc-man-city.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh nh\u01b0 Guendouzi c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLichtsteiner v\u00e0o thay Maitland-Niles ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong hi\u1ec7p 1 v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t. Lichtsteiner l\u00e0m tr\u00f2n vai trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 khi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 pha c\u1eaft b\u00f3ng k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGuendouzi cho th\u1ea5y t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ea7m nh\u1ecbp, \u0111i\u1ec1u ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i n\u00e0o. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 19, anh v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u pha b\u00f3ng non n\u1edbt v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u1ec1m tin n\u01a1i c\u00e1c v\u1ec7 tinh xung quanh. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Torreira \u1edf 20 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i sau khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 h\u1ecd bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 HLV Emery c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh. B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh l\u00e0 m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c nh\u1eefng n\u01a1i kh\u00e1c v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong ch\u1edbp m\u1eaft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Arsenal 0-2 Man City\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Arsenal 0-2 Man City\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/Thong-so-Arsenal.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Arsenal 0-2 Man City</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Arsenal 0-2 Man City (V\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19):<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278994\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/08/13/arsenal-mancity-.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"340\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Arsenal 0-2 Man City tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/gary-neville-noi-ve-tran-arsenal-02-man-city-172-194351.html\">C\u1ef1u sao M.U n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Arsenal 0-2 Man City?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sterling-ly-giai-man-an-mung-khieu-khich-o-tran-gap-arsenal-172-194350.html\">Sterling l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i m\u00e0n \u0103n m\u1eebng khi\u00eau kh\u00edch tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cech-thua-man-city-giup-arsenal-truong-thanh-hon-172-194349.html\">Cech: Tr\u1eadn thua Man City gi\u00fap Arsenal tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-arsenal-02-man-city-172-194347.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn Arsenal 0-2 Man City</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2285","checkdouble":"194359"},{"date":"16:08 12/08","title":"HLV Sarri ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi Chelsea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/hlv-sarri-tiec-nuoi-khi-chelsea-khong-the-ky-hop-dong-voi-cai-ten-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Maurizio Sarri n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Gonzalo Higuain, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Higuain</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Maurizio Sarri nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gonzalo Higuain l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia t\u1eebng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf Napoli, \u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Higuain nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Maurizio Sarri n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Gonzalo Higuain h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Maurizio Sarri n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Gonzalo Higuain h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/hlv-sarri-tiec-nuoi-khi-chelsea-khong-the-ky-hop-dong-voi-cai-ten-nay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Higuain</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 58 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u1edf s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-sap-co-tien-dao-tri-gia-53-trieu-bang-172-190389.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mua Higuain</span> \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Morata.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn Italia \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGonzalo Higuain sau \u0111\u00f3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn AC Milan theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi bu\u1ed9c HLV Sarri ph\u1ea3i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111ang c\u00f3 trong tay.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Sarri ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u00ec Chelsea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua Higuain</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Maurizio Sarri n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Gonzalo Higuain, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Higuain se lai nhuong san khau cho Ronaldo\" title=\"Higuain s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0\u1eddng s\u00e2n kh\u1ea5u cho Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/Juventus-len-tieng-vu-ban-Higuain-cho-AC-Milan-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u00ec Chelsea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua Higuain\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Higuain l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Chelsea, t\u00f4i tin c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t Courtois, song BL\u0110 \u0111\u00e3 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Kepa Arrizabalaga \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i tin Kepa s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi Mateo Kovacic v\u00e0 Jorginho\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cV\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n, t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u00f3 trong tay m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00fap Chelsea gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Sarri \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, theo \u0111\u00f3 Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Huddersfield trong khu\u00f4n\u00a0kh\u1ed5 v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2284","checkdouble":"194318"},{"date":"15:59 12/08","title":"Danh th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i AFF Cup 2018?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/danh-thu-nhat-ban-se-doi-dau-tuyen-viet-nam-tai-aff-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Campuchia m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Keisuke Honda v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean CLB Melbourne Victory n\u00f3i ri\u00eang v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u00f3i chung b\u1edfi l\u1ebd Keisuke Honda th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0a ra tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1eeba \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho CLB Melbourne City \u1edf gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia Australia sau k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Keisuke Honda l\u00e0m gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Campuchia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Keisuke Honda l\u00e0m gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Campuchia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/df.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Campuchia t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c l\u1ec5 ra m\u1eaft t\u00e2n Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia. \u1ea2nh: CNCC.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y chia s\u1ebb: \"T\u00f4i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho CLB n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Melbourne Victory l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng hay nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Australia. T\u00f4i t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng nhau, ch\u00fang ta h\u00e3y bi\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u1eabu v\u1eady, nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u n\u00e0y gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ngh\u0129a b\u1edfi theo CNCC, Keisuke Honda \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c h\u1ee7y b\u1ecf h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p HLV khi c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a Melbourne Victory \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i t\u1eebng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Honda kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh m\u00e0u \u00e1o m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Prak Sovannara \u0111ang t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi gi\u1eef v\u1ecb tr\u00ed thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia Campuchia sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a HLV Leonardo Vitorino ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil. Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Keisuke Honda th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gia nh\u1eadp CLB Melbourne Victory, Honda t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Mexico trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Pachuca. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i 32, anh v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, khi \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y v\u00e0o t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Keisuke Honda l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c1 t\u1eebng chinh chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. \u0110\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 CSKA Moscow v\u00e0 AC Milan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Honda t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia Campuchia s\u1ebd l\u00e0 AFF Cup 2018 di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 11 t\u1edbi, n\u01a1i h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Zing.vn<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2283","checkdouble":"194319"},{"date":"16:39 12/08","title":"Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c v\u1ee5 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/17/tiet-lo-cuc-soc-vu-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-den-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Chelsea, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh bom t\u1ea5n 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, v\u00e0 Kepa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ca ng\u1ee3i h\u1ebft l\u1eddi.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nKepa g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong khung g\u1ed7<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">G\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp n\u00e0o, k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp The Blues \u0111\u1ebfn khi ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kepa \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng trong 90 ph\u00fat, gi\u00fap Chelsea th\u1eafng ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng Huddersfield v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a bom t\u1ea5n, trung v\u1ec7 Antonio Rudiger cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Kepa \u0111ang l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng li\u00ean l\u1ea1c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 khi n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t, v\u00e0 v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1eadn t\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kepa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ca ng\u1ee3i h\u1ebft l\u1eddi sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Huddersfield\" title=\"Kepa vs Huddersfield\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/giu-sach-luoi-thu-mon-71-trieu-bang-duoc-dong-doi-ca-ngoi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kepa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ca ng\u1ee3i h\u1ebft l\u1eddi sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Huddersfield</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Nh\u00ecn chung, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Chelsea hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Thibaut Courtois, nh\u01b0ng anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc. T\u00f4i ch\u00fac Thibaut g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u may m\u1eafn t\u1ea1i Real Madrid, nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Kepa &ndash; th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi phong th\u00e1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0, trung v\u1ec7 tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t giai \u0111o\u1ea1n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, nh\u01b0ng Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t trong ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y. 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi &ndash; nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Th\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp thu chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a HLV Maurizio Sarri, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t&rdquo; &ndash; Rudiger k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1, vi\u1ec7c Kepa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ca ng\u1ee3i h\u1ebft l\u1eddi s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn anh ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng t\u1ef1 tin trong vi\u1ec7c h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp t\u1ea1i m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278917\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/08/11/huddersfield-chelsea.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"340\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-thang-hoanh-trang-chua-the-mung-voi-nhung-diem-yeu-chet-nguoi-172-194288.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/chelsea-thang-hoanh-trang-chua-the-mung-voi-nhung-diem-yeu-chet-nguoi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-thang-hoanh-trang-chua-the-mung-voi-nhung-diem-yeu-chet-nguoi-172-194288.html\">Chelsea th\u1eafng ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng: Ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 m\u1eebng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu ch\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1eddi</span><br>\r\nTrong ni\u1ec1m h\u00e2n hoan gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, Chelsea b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 y\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Huddersfield v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn HLV Sarri r\u1ea5t \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-huddersfield-03-chelsea-172-194286.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-huddersfield-03-chelsea.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-huddersfield-03-chelsea-172-194286.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Huddersfield 0-3 Chelsea</span><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Huddersfield v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Huddersfield vs Chelsea v\u00f2ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sarri-chi-ra-2-diem-yeu-cua-chelsea-o-tran-gap-huddersfield-172-194299.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/sarri-chi-ra-2-diem-yeu-cua-chelsea-o-tran-gap-huddersfield.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sarri-chi-ra-2-diem-yeu-cua-chelsea-o-tran-gap-huddersfield-172-194299.html\">Sarri ch\u1ec9 ra 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Huddersfield</span><br>\r\nHLV Maurizio Sarri v\u1eeba ch\u1ec9 ra 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n Chelsea c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng Huddersfield.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2282","checkdouble":"194320"},{"date":"17:04 12/08","title":"\"Arsenal c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u1eb1m trong nh\u00f3m xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng sau 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/arsenal-co-the-nam-trong-nhom-xuong-hang-sau-2-vong-dau-dau-tien.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Paul Merson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 lo ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1ebd r\u01a1i xu\u1ed1ng nh\u00f3m cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng sau hai v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Paul Merson lo s\u1ee3 Arsenal tr\u1eafng tay sau 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19 kh\u00f4ng \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Arsenal, ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 Man City. D\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 th\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London v\u1eabn b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paul Merson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Paul Merson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/arsenal-co-the-nam-trong-nhom-xuong-hang-sau-2-vong-dau-dau-tien.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Paul Merson lo ng\u1ea1i Arsenal s\u1ebd t\u1ee5t xu\u1ed1ng nh\u00f3m cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng sau 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf NHA</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Man City, Arsenal ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eb7p th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n n\u1eefa. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Chelsea, trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7 \u1edf Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPaul Merson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 lo ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1ebd r\u01a1i xu\u1ed1ng nh\u00f3m cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng sau hai v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cUnai Emery c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ng\u00e1n ng\u1ea9m nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Man City sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Arsenal r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cEmery m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn Anh, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i lo s\u1ee3 r\u1eb1ng Arsenal s\u1ebd r\u01a1i xu\u1ed1ng nh\u00f3m cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng sau hai v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Paul Merson ca ng\u1ee3i k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Emery</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City v\u00e0 Arsenal, song Paul Merson \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khen ng\u1ee3i k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua s\u1eafm c\u1ee7a HLV Unai Emery.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Unai Emery\" title=\"HLV Unai Emery\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/emery-quyet-tam-chan-dung-mach-thua-truoc-guardiola.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Paul Merson ca ng\u1ee3i HLV Unai Emery</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cEmery \u0111\u00e3 mang \u0111\u1ebfn Sokratis Papastathopoulos, Stephan Lichtsteiner, Lucas Torreira, Bern Leno v\u00e0 Matteo Guendouzi. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 mua nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 Arsenal c\u1ea7n. Arsenal c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m, Sokratis v\u00e0 Lichtsteiner l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung h\u1ee3p l\u00fd\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cKh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 34 hay 35 nh\u01b0 Lichtsteiner ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i tin \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u00f4ng minh c\u1ee7a Arsenal. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Lichtsteiner s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ed1i nay, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-arsenal-vs-man-city-22h-ngay-128-khac-biet-o-nen-tang-172-194293.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp Man City</span> trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018, d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 nh\u01b0ng Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n n\u1eeda xanh th\u00e0nh Manchester.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2281","checkdouble":"194321"},{"date":"16:21 12/08","title":"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Gerard Pique chia tay s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/chinh-thuc-gerard-pique-chia-tay-su-nghiep-quoc-te.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, trung v\u1ec7 Pique x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn chia tay \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha, sau khi c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi HLV Enrique.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nPique t\u1eeb gi\u00e3 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, nh\u01b0ng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga, b\u1edfi scandal c\u1ee7a HLV julen Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Sau gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u1ee7a B\u00f2 t\u00f3t \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i b\u0103m v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u00e0o n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, trung v\u1ec7 Gerard Pique l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn chia tay \u0110T, sau khi c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi t\u00e2n HLV Luis Enrique. Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c suy ngh\u0129 trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Luis Enrique m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc&rdquo; &ndash; Pique cho bi\u1ebft. &ldquo;\u00d4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ecdi cho t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecfi th\u0103m t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh \u1ea5p \u1ee7 t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 suy ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trung v\u1ec7 Pique x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn chia tay \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha\" title=\"Pique gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/chinh-thuc-gerard-pique-chia-tay-su-nghiep-quoc-te.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Trung v\u1ec7 Pique x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn chia tay \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Th\u1eadt l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u00fd \u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb9p trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia, khi t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup v\u00e0 EURO. Nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung cho Barcelona. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n v\u00e0i n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho CLB c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh&rdquo; &ndash; Pique x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn chia tay \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o B\u00f2 t\u00f3t, trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 102 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n, ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Anh g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha, gi\u00e0nh World Cup 2010 t\u1ea1i Nam Phi v\u00e0 EURO 2 n\u0103m sau \u0111\u00f3. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t, T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Barca \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Andres Iniesta.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sevilla-to-cao-barca-truoc-sieu-cup-tay-ban-nha-180-194300.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/sevilla-to-cao-barca-truoc-sieu-cup-tay-ban-nha.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sevilla-to-cao-barca-truoc-sieu-cup-tay-ban-nha-180-194300.html\">Sevilla t\u1ed1 Barca \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u00ean v\u1ecb t\u1ea1i Si\u00eau c\u00fap TBN</span><br>\r\nSevilla t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o Barca tr\u01b0\u1edbc Si\u00eau c\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Andalusia tin r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed b\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Barcelona th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-chot-tuong-lai-ousmane-dembele-180-194312.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/barca-chot-tuong-lai-ousmane-dembele.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-chot-tuong-lai-ousmane-dembele-180-194312.html\">Barca ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ousmane Dembele</span><br>\r\nT\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ousmane Dembele \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, theo ESPN \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nhan-dinh-sevilla-vs-barca-3h-ngay-138-co-messi-la-co-tat-ca-180-194294.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/nhan-dinh-sevilla-vs-barca-3h-ngay-138-co-messi-la-co-tat-ca.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nhan-dinh-sevilla-vs-barca-3h-ngay-138-co-messi-la-co-tat-ca-180-194294.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sevilla vs Barca (3h ng\u00e0y 13/8): C\u00f3 Messi l\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3</span><br>\r\nBarcelona m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 si\u00eau sao Lionel Messi. Nh\u01b0ng khi s\u1ed1 10 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2280","checkdouble":"194322"}]}